pageTitle: Itinerary for Wednesday, January 30, 2019 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Ottawa, Ontario

10:00 a.m. The Prime Minister will attend the National Caucus meeting.

Room 025B
West Block
Parliament Hill  

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

4:30 p.m. The Prime Minister will meet with President of the Canadian Labour Congress Hassan Yussuff.

Closed to media.
